    <string name="info_flight_time_text">Make the game feel faster or slower by changing the default time the ball stays in the air (from hit to bounce on opponent\'s side). Swing force and phone tilt will increase or decrease this time.\n\n%1$d-%2$dms: Hard (Fast)\n%3$d-%4$dms: Medium\n%5$d-%6$dms: Easy (Slow)\n\n(Synced with opponent)\n\n**Note**: In Solo Rally mode, an additional 500ms is added to flight time (adjustable in Advanced settings).</string>
