    <string name="info_hit_window_text">Sets the base total time window you have to hit the ball. Harder shots (like Smashes) from your opponent may shrink this window further.\n\nLarger Window = Easier\nSmaller Window = Harder\n\nRange: %1$dms (Hard) to %2$dms (Easy)\n\n(Synced with opponent)</string>
    <string name="shrinking_hit_window">Shrinking Hit Window</string>
    <string name="info_shrinking_window_title">Shrinking Hit Window</string>
    <string name="info_shrinking_window_text">If enabled, the hit window shrinks slightly with each consecutive rally hit, making longer rallies progressively harder.\n\n(Synced with opponent)</string>
    <string name="info_rally_no_risk_text">In Rally Mode, net and out risks are eliminated since players are cooperating. Difficulty comes solely from timing windows.</string>

